    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>时间已然崩坏。世界也同样支离破碎。但或许，你能修复这一切。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Autonomica</strong>是一款可单人或联机游玩的开放世界生存游戏，汲取太阳朋克美学精髓，以农耕、<strong>自动化生产有机产品</strong>、探索与未来科技为驱动核心。建造能大规模生产番茄的自动化农场，研发先进机械，探索充满谜团、奇异现象与时空扭曲挑战的岛屿。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>AUTONOMICA的世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们构建的世界以清洁能源为基石——从温馨农场到太阳能巨型工厂。所有任务（灌溉作物、采集资源或运营生产线）均可手动完成，适合热爱亲力亲为的玩家。当您选择启用自动化时，即可优化日常流程，将时间投入探索、建造，并按您自己的节奏塑造世界。培育有机作物，制造合成产品，逐步扩张您的农业帝国。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/95188d8b4fa4e4556f78c3b3e90ad1a0.poster.avif?t=1770909104\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/95188d8b4fa4e4556f78c3b3e90ad1a0.webm?t=1770909104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/95188d8b4fa4e4556f78c3b3e90ad1a0.mp4?t=1770909104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>不同于记忆中的农耕</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >忘却宁静的田园日常吧。这是个拥有实时天气、季节更替与鲜活昼夜循环系统的动态世界。作物需要光照、温度与水分才能茁壮生长。通过创建最佳培育环境提升产量，实时监控植物幸福指数、效率与品质等级。想要更优质的番茄？那就善待它们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/b4ea0daf24a506735e2c7aa199dc7b52.poster.avif?t=1770909104\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/b4ea0daf24a506735e2c7aa199dc7b52.webm?t=1770909104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/b4ea0daf24a506735e2c7aa199dc7b52.mp4?t=1770909104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🛠<strong> 建造与自动化</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<i>Autonomica</i>中，您将利用自然资源驱动庞大生产线。运用结构方块、机械与传送带系统，实现作物培育、产品制造乃至动物饲养的全流程自动化。从简易番茄复制器到全功能处理中心——所有系统皆由您设计优化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/d76caea222b63ddfbe0808cdedc35a50.poster.avif?t=1770909104\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/d76caea222b63ddfbe0808cdedc35a50.webm?t=1770909104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/d76caea222b63ddfbe0808cdedc35a50.mp4?t=1770909104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>科技赋能未来</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁跨领域研究站科技：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>设计台</strong>——自动化建造、能源与机械系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>植物室</strong>——升级作物、动物与培育技术</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>烹饪站</strong>——将天然原料转化为高价值食品</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您的工坊既是创新实验室，也是生存要塞。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/a3d255a862bcb8f2dc890f64ebac8052.avif?t=1770909104\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自定义世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>Autonomica</strong>中，建造系统完全模块化，且由玩家主导。无论打造温馨小屋、流线型温室，还是嵌入山体的自动化枢纽——每栋建筑都始于您的创意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/aae96b86964dbc1d4bdfee30d1fda821.poster.avif?t=1770909104\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/aae96b86964dbc1d4bdfee30d1fda821.webm?t=1770909104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/aae96b86964dbc1d4bdfee30d1fda821.mp4?t=1770909104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用家具、配色与布局精心设计您的家园。合理摆放装饰品可激活房间加成，影响属性、人际关系与NPC互动。从阳光卧室到尖端实验室——您的空间彰显您的游戏风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/79f2b32045b5b04bed706f7e8bffc481.poster.avif?t=1770909104\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/79f2b32045b5b04bed706f7e8bffc481.webm?t=1770909104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/79f2b32045b5b04bed706f7e8bffc481.mp4?t=1770909104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>幽灵主宰的夜晚</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >日落时分，它们便会降临。<br>幽灵，即时空裂隙实验所诞生的不稳定存在，正游荡于森林深处。追踪它们、与之战斗，并利用水压爆破枪和原型电弧枪等高科技工具捕捉它们的精华。将其原子化形态存储于<strong>纳米容器</strong>中，利用其能量强化您的生产线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/fe7fddeb73243fbd64d9bd0e00bca8b0.poster.avif?t=1770909104\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/fe7fddeb73243fbd64d9bd0e00bca8b0.webm?t=1770909104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/fe7fddeb73243fbd64d9bd0e00bca8b0.mp4?t=1770909104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>穿越时空之旅</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过<strong>时空胶囊</strong>闯入不稳定时间线，挑战三大高风险模式：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>开采模式</strong>——限时奖励的和平探索</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PVE模式</strong>——对抗危险幽灵与强力Boss</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PVP模式</strong>——在生存竞技场与其他玩家及幽灵角逐</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若能生还，稀有作物、动物与科技将伴您凯旋。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/7e47940100e9ea896c65c9a2c33db105.poster.avif?t=1770909104\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/7e47940100e9ea896c65c9a2c33db105.webm?t=1770909104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/7e47940100e9ea896c65c9a2c33db105.mp4?t=1770909104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌎<strong> 宏大开放世界</strong>——无加载界面与强制睡眠机制；探索各种手工打造的生态区，其中布满秘密、资源与无尽奇遇。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎶<strong> 浪漫复古科幻&amp;合成波</strong>——沉浸于怀旧浪漫氛围中，复古电子设备与时尚美学交织，配以动人合成波原声。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨<strong> 角色定制</strong>——创建专属角色，培养技能，在迷人的本地商店解锁独特发型、服饰与配饰。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌱<strong> 农耕与畜牧</strong>——培育100+种作物变体，饲养可互动的动物，建造无需微操的自运行生态农场。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚙️<strong> 深度自动化系统</strong>——简洁的传送带设计优雅融入太阳朋克美学，整合电网与动态水管系统，实现从乳品厂到无人机配送的全流程自动化。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧱<strong> 精细建造系统</strong>——从巨型建筑到温馨家园自由建造，定制室内装饰，打造完美生活空间。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏗️<strong> 动态环境</strong>——协助NPC修复建筑、复兴商业、升级城镇，见证社区因您的贡献而繁荣。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧑<strong>‍</strong>🤝<strong>‍</strong>🧑<strong> NPC与关系系统</strong>——与动态NPC建立友谊、爱情或婚姻关系，他们会真实响应您的行为、着装与进度。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⛈️<strong> 动态天气与季节</strong>——体验无缝昼夜循环与雨雪雾等天气事件，全程无加载。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🛸<strong> 载具与探索</strong>——驾驶悬浮滑板、越野车和强力机甲穿越岛屿，发掘隐藏秘密。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👻<strong> 幽灵狩猎与夜间探险</strong>——勇闯黑暗狩猎幽灵，捕获神秘能量解锁强力科技。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⏳<strong>时空冒险</strong>——穿越破碎时间线，探索充满独特生物与作物的平行世界，通过揭开过去秘密影响未来。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🕹️<strong> 多人游戏&amp;PvEvP模式</strong>——单人冒险或组队探索，在PvEvP开采模式中跨时间线争夺战利品。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮<strong> 自由选择玩法</strong>——从休闲探索到硬核生存，体验由您定义。支持直观操作与自定义难度，PvP、PvE或创意模式任君选择。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤝<strong> 协作自动化</strong>——与好友共建自动化农场、工厂与繁荣的定居点，联手管理庞大产业链。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤔<strong> 我们好像漏掉了什么</strong>——还有更多惊喜功能正在开发中，我们正与时间赛跑，可能还有些超酷内容暂未列出！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/511af5e7acb018ae7c22c0186fcc1a76.poster.avif?t=1770909104\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/511af5e7acb018ae7c22c0186fcc1a76.webm?t=1770909104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895160/extras/511af5e7acb018ae7c22c0186fcc1a76.mp4?t=1770909104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
